Title: Birth Day
Writer: Bruce Miller (teleplay by), Margaret Atwood (based on the novel by), Bruce Miller (created for television by)
Actors: Elisabeth Moss, Joseph Fiennes, Yvonne Strahovski, Alexis Bledel
Plot: Offred and her fellow Handmaids assist with the delivery of Janine's baby, prompting Offred to recall her own daughter's birth. Offred draws closer to Ofglen while dreading a secret meeting with the Commander.
